    "text": "The most liberating thing for me has been to go with the flow and _just do it_ even if I'm using dirty tricks like `eval` and processing code with regexes and stuff. Learning the value of just coding for fun. The slippy mindset!\n\n...and apparently I code spreadsheets for fun now.",
